      <title>жөӢиҜ•дҝ®ж”№</title>
      <link href="hello-world/"/>
      <url>hello-world/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>[toc]<br>д»Ӣз»Қд»Ӣз»Қ</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="дёҖ-дҫқиө–жЈҖжҹҘ"><a href="#дёҖ-дҫқиө–жЈҖжҹҘ" class="headerlink" title="дёҖ дҫқиө–жЈҖжҹҘ"></a>дёҖ дҫқиө–жЈҖжҹҘ</h2><p>д»Ҙcentos7дёәдҫӢ</p><h3 id="1-иҪҜд»¶"><a href="#1-иҪҜд»¶" class="headerlink" title="1. иҪҜд»¶"></a>1. иҪҜд»¶</h3><p><a href="https://docs.cloudera.com/documentation/enterprise/6/release-notes/topics/rg_os_requirements.html">https://docs.cloudera.com/documentation/enterprise/6/release-notes/topics/rg_os_requirements.html</a></p><h4 id="0-еёёз”ЁиҪҜд»¶е®үиЈ…"><a href="#0-еёёз”ЁиҪҜд»¶е®үиЈ…" class="headerlink" title="0. еёёз”ЁиҪҜд»¶е®үиЈ…"></a>0. еёёз”ЁиҪҜд»¶е®үиЈ…</h4><p>жӯӨжӯҘйӘӨйқһеҝ…йЎ»</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum install -y bind-utils</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="1-python"><a href="#1-python" class="headerlink" title="1. python"></a>1. python</h4><p>дҪҝз”Ё2.7зүҲжң¬жҲ–д»ҘдёҠзүҲжң¬пјҢдҪҶдёҚж”ҜжҢҒ3<br>centos7 дёӯй»ҳи®Өе·ІеҢ…еҗ«пјҢеҰӮжһңжңүеӨҡзүҲжң¬йңҖи®ҫзҪ®PYSPARK_PYTHONе’Ң<br>PYSPARK_DRIVER_PYTHONзҺҜеўғеҸҳйҮҸ</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> жҹҘзңӢзүҲжң¬</span></span><br><span class="line">python --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2-Perl"><a href="#2-Perl" class="headerlink" title="2. Perl"></a>2. Perl</h4><p>дёҖиҲ¬е·Іе®үиЈ…</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> жҹҘзңӢзүҲжң¬</span></span><br><span class="line">perlВ -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="3-python-psycopg2"><a href="#3-python-psycopg2" class="headerlink" title="3. python-psycopg2"></a>3. python-psycopg2</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> иҰҒе…Ҳе®үиЈ…epel-releaseпјҢпјҢиҝҷдёӘеҢ…еҢ…еҗ«дәҶ EPEL жәҗзҡ„ gpg еҜҶй’Ҙе’ҢиҪҜд»¶жәҗдҝЎжҒҜпјҢиҜҘиҪҜд»¶еҢ…дјҡиҮӘеҠЁй…ҚзҪ®yumзҡ„иҪҜд»¶д»“еә“</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> еҗҰеҲҷдёӢдёҖжӯҘдјҡжҸҗзӨәпјҡжІЎжңүеҸҜз”ЁиҪҜд»¶еҢ… pip-python</span></span><br><span class="line">yum -y install epel-release</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> е®үиЈ…pip</span></span><br><span class="line">yum -y install python-pip</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> дҪҝз”Ёpip е®үиЈ… psycopg2</span></span><br><span class="line">pip install psycopg2==2.7.5 --ignore-installed</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-зҪ‘з»ң"><a href="#2-зҪ‘з»ң" class="headerlink" title="2. зҪ‘з»ң"></a>2. зҪ‘з»ң</h3><h4 id="зҰҒз”Ёipv6"><a href="#зҰҒз”Ёipv6" class="headerlink" title="зҰҒз”Ёipv6"></a>зҰҒз”Ёipv6</h4><p><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/225d040d0b66">https://www.jianshu.com/p/225d040d0b66</a></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sysctl -w net.ipv6.conf.all.disable_ipv6=1</span><br><span class="line">sysctl -w net.ipv6.conf.default.disable_ipv6=1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">reboot</span><br><span class="line">netstat -lnpt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="й…ҚзҪ®hostname"><a href="#й…ҚзҪ®hostname" class="headerlink" title="й…ҚзҪ®hostname"></a>й…ҚзҪ®hostname</h4><p><a href="https://docs.cloudera.com/documentation/enterprise/6/latest/topics/configure_network_names.html">https://docs.cloudera.com/documentation/enterprise/6/latest/topics/configure_network_names.html</a><br>з”Ёе…Ёз§°еҹҹеҗҚпјҢеҰӮпјҡpaas-201.adp.com иҖҢдёҚжҳҜ paas-201</p><ol><li>й…ҚзҪ®hostname<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo hostnamectl set-hostname foo-1.example.com</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>зј–иҫ‘/ets/hosts(йӣҶзҫӨз»ҹдёҖ)<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1.1.1.1  foo-1.example.com  foo-1</span><br><span class="line">2.2.2.2  foo-2.example.com  foo-2</span><br><span class="line">3.3.3.3  foo-3.example.com  foo-3</span><br><span class="line">4.4.4.4  foo-4.example.com  foo-4</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>зј–иҫ‘/etc/sysconfig/network<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">echo &quot;HOSTNAME=$HOSTNAME&quot; &gt;&gt;/etc/sysconfig/network</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="е…ій—ӯйҳІзҒ«еўҷ"><a href="#е…ій—ӯйҳІзҒ«еўҷ" class="headerlink" title="е…ій—ӯйҳІзҒ«еўҷ"></a>е…ій—ӯйҳІзҒ«еўҷ</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> дҝқеӯҳи§„еҲҷ</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo iptables-save &gt; ~/firewall.rules</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> е…ій—ӯ</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo systemctl disable firewalld</span><br><span class="line">sudo systemctl stop firewalld</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-е…ій—ӯSELinux"><a href="#3-е…ій—ӯSELinux" class="headerlink" title="3. е…ій—ӯSELinux"></a>3. е…ій—ӯSELinux</h3>жҹҘзңӢжҳҜеҗҰе·Із»Ҹе…ій—ӯ<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">getenforce</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>е…ій—ӯж–№жі•пјҡ<br>дҝ®ж”№/etc/selinux/config<br>SELINUX=permissive<br>е№¶жү§иЎҢ setenforce 0  з«ӢеҚіз”ҹж•Ҳ<h3 id="4-еҗҜз”Ёntp"><a href="#4-еҗҜз”Ёntp" class="headerlink" title="4. еҗҜз”Ёntp"></a>4. еҗҜз”Ёntp</h3>е®үиЈ…еҗҺз”Ёд»ҘдёӢе‘Ҫд»ӨиҝӣиЎҢйӘҢиҜҒ<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl status chronyd.service </span><br><span class="line">chronyc sources -v </span><br><span class="line">chronyc sourcestats -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="дәҢ-е®үиЈ…"><a href="#дәҢ-е®үиЈ…" class="headerlink" title="дәҢ е®үиЈ…"></a>дәҢ е®үиЈ…</h2><h3 id="дёҖ-й…ҚзҪ®жң¬ең°д»“еә“"><a href="#дёҖ-й…ҚзҪ®жң¬ең°д»“еә“" class="headerlink" title="дёҖ. й…ҚзҪ®жң¬ең°д»“еә“"></a>дёҖ. й…ҚзҪ®жң¬ең°д»“еә“</h3><a href="https://docs.cloudera.com/documentation/enterprise/6/latest/topics/cm_ig_create_local_package_repo.html">https://docs.cloudera.com/documentation/enterprise/6/latest/topics/cm_ig_create_local_package_repo.html</a><h4 id="1-й…ҚзҪ®webжңҚеҠЎеҷЁ"><a href="#1-й…ҚзҪ®webжңҚеҠЎеҷЁ" class="headerlink" title="1. й…ҚзҪ®webжңҚеҠЎеҷЁ"></a>1. й…ҚзҪ®webжңҚеҠЎеҷЁ</h4></li><li>е®үиЈ…<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo yum install httpd</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>йңҖдҝқиҜҒ/var/wwwзЈҒзӣҳз©әй—ҙи¶іеӨҹпјҢе»әи®®жҢӮиҪҪпјҢиҝҷйҮҢеҒҮи®ҫ /home/www жңүи¶іеӨҹзҡ„з©әй—ҙ<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mv /var/www /var/www2</span><br><span class="line">mkdir /home/www</span><br><span class="line">ln -s /home/www /var/www</span><br><span class="line">mv /var/www2/* /var/www/</span><br><span class="line">rm -rf /var/www2</span><br><span class="line">ls /home/www</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>еҗҜеҠЁ<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo systemctl start httpd</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2-дёӢиҪҪж–Үд»¶-clouderaManagerе’Ңcdhпјү"><a href="#2-дёӢиҪҪж–Үд»¶-clouderaManagerе’Ңcdhпјү" class="headerlink" title="2. дёӢиҪҪж–Үд»¶(clouderaManagerе’Ңcdhпјү"></a>2. дёӢиҪҪж–Үд»¶(clouderaManagerе’Ңcdhпјү</h4></li><li>clouderaManager<br>дёӢиҪҪпјҡ<a href="https://archive.cloudera.com/cm6/6.3.1/repo-as-tarball/cm6.3.1-redhat7.tar.gz">https://archive.cloudera.com/cm6/6.3.1/repo-as-tarball/cm6.3.1-redhat7.tar.gz</a></li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo mkdir -p /var/www/html/cloudera-repos/cm6</span><br><span class="line">tar xvfz cm6.3.1-redhat7.tar.gz -C /var/www/html/cloudera-repos/cm6 --strip-components=1</span><br><span class="line">sudo chmod -R ugo+rX /var/www/html/cloudera-repos/cm6</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li>cdh</li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo mkdir -p /var/www/html/cloudera-repos</span><br><span class="line">sudo wget --recursive --no-parent --no-host-directories https://archive.cloudera.com/cdh6/6.3.2/redhat7/ -P /var/www/html/cloudera-repos</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo wget --recursive --no-parent --no-host-directories https://archive.cloudera.com/gplextras6/6.3.2/redhat7/ -P /var/www/html/cloudera-repos</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo chmod -R ugo+rX /var/www/html/cloudera-repos/cdh6</span><br><span class="line">sudo chmod -R ugo+rX /var/www/html/cloudera-repos/gplextras6</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>и®ҝй—® http://<host>/cloudera-repos/ пјҢеә”иҜҘеҸҜд»ҘзңӢеҲ°дёӢиҪҪзҡ„ж–Үд»¶</p><h4 id="3-й…ҚзҪ®дҪҝз”Ёжң¬ең°еӯҳеӮЁеә“"><a href="#3-й…ҚзҪ®дҪҝз”Ёжң¬ең°еӯҳеӮЁеә“" class="headerlink" title="3. й…ҚзҪ®дҪҝз”Ёжң¬ең°еӯҳеӮЁеә“"></a>3. й…ҚзҪ®дҪҝз”Ёжң¬ең°еӯҳеӮЁеә“</h4><p>еҲӣе»ә/etc/yum.repos.d/cloudera-repo.repo<br>еҶ…е®№еҰӮдёӢпјҡ</p><p>[cloudera-repo]<br>name=cloudera-repo<br>baseurl=<a href="http://paas-241/cloudera-repos/cm6">http://paas-241/cloudera-repos/cm6</a><br>enabled=1<br>gpgcheck=0</p><h3 id="дёү-е®үиЈ…CDH"><a href="#дёү-е®үиЈ…CDH" class="headerlink" title="дёү. е®үиЈ…CDH"></a>дёү. е®үиЈ…CDH</h3><h4 id="1-е®үиЈ…java"><a href="#1-е®үиЈ…java" class="headerlink" title="1. е®үиЈ…java"></a>1. е®үиЈ…java</h4> <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum install -y oracle-j2sdk1.8</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2-е®үиЈ…CM"><a href="#2-е®үиЈ…CM" class="headerlink" title="2. е®үиЈ…CM"></a>2. е®үиЈ…CM</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum install -y cloudera-manager-daemons cloudera-manager-agent cloudera-manager-server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="3-е®үиЈ…ж•°жҚ®еә“"><a href="#3-е®үиЈ…ж•°жҚ®еә“" class="headerlink" title="3. е®үиЈ…ж•°жҚ®еә“"></a>3. е®үиЈ…ж•°жҚ®еә“</h4><p>еҒҮи®ҫдҪҝз”Ёmysqlдё”е·Іе®үиЈ…</p><p>еңЁcmжңҚеҠЎеҷЁдёҠпјҡ</p><h5 id="1-е®үиЈ…jdbcй©ұеҠЁ"><a href="#1-е®үиЈ…jdbcй©ұеҠЁ" class="headerlink" title="1. е®үиЈ…jdbcй©ұеҠЁ"></a>1. е®үиЈ…jdbcй©ұеҠЁ</h5><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget https://dev.mysql.com/get/Downloads/Connector-J/mysql-connector-java-5.1.46.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">tar zxvf mysql-connector-java-5.1.46.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo mkdir -p /usr/share/java/</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">cd mysql-connector-java-5.1.46</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo cp mysql-connector-java-5.1.46-bin.jar  /usr/share/java/mysql-connector-java.jar</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="2-еҲӣе»әж•°жҚ®еә“е№¶жҺҲжқғ"><a href="#2-еҲӣе»әж•°жҚ®еә“е№¶жҺҲжқғ" class="headerlink" title="2. еҲӣе»әж•°жҚ®еә“е№¶жҺҲжқғ"></a>2. еҲӣе»әж•°жҚ®еә“е№¶жҺҲжқғ</h5><p>зҷ»еҪ•mysqlиҝӣиЎҢй…ҚзҪ®пјҡ</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mysql -u root -h 192.168.100.200 -p</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>жү§иЎҢд»ҘдёӢе‘Ҫд»ӨпјҡеҒҮи®ҫж•°жҚ®еә“дёәcdh жҺҲжқғз”ЁжҲ·дёәrootпјҢеҜҶз Ғдёәanyonedev<br> <figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">CREATE</span> DATABASE cdh <span class="keyword">DEFAULT</span> <span class="type">CHARACTER</span> <span class="keyword">SET</span> utf8 <span class="keyword">DEFAULT</span> <span class="keyword">COLLATE</span> utf8_general_ci;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">GRANT</span> <span class="keyword">ALL</span> <span class="keyword">ON</span> cdh.<span class="operator">*</span> <span class="keyword">TO</span> <span class="string">&#x27;root&#x27;</span>@<span class="string">&#x27;%&#x27;</span> IDENTIFIED <span class="keyword">BY</span> <span class="string">&#x27;anyonedev&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SHOW</span> DATABASES;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SHOW</span> GRANTS <span class="keyword">FOR</span> <span class="string">&#x27;root&#x27;</span>@<span class="string">&#x27;%&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h5 id="3-жү§иЎҢеҲӣе»әи„ҡжң¬"><a href="#3-жү§иЎҢеҲӣе»әи„ҡжң¬" class="headerlink" title="3. жү§иЎҢеҲӣе»әи„ҡжң¬"></a>3. жү§иЎҢеҲӣе»әи„ҡжң¬</h5><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">/opt/cloudera/cm/schema/scm_prepare_database.sh -h 192.168.100.200 mysql cdh root anyonedev</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="еӣӣ-еҗҜеҠЁ"><a href="#еӣӣ-еҗҜеҠЁ" class="headerlink" title="еӣӣ еҗҜеҠЁ"></a>еӣӣ еҗҜеҠЁ</h4> <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo systemctl enable cloudera-scm-server</span><br><span class="line">sudo systemctl start cloudera-scm-server</span><br><span class="line">sudo tail -f /var/log/cloudera-scm-server/cloudera-scm-server.log</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>зӣҙеҲ°зңӢеҲ°пјҡ<br>INFO WebServerImpl:com.cloudera.server.cmf.WebServerImpl: Started Jetty server.<br>еҲҷиҜҙжҳҺеҗҜеҠЁе®ҢжҲҗпјҢжү“ејҖ<br><a href="http://paas-241:7180/">http://paas-241:7180</a> еҚіеҸҜ admin/admin</p><p>жіЁж„Ҹй…ҚзҪ®иҮӘе®ҡд№үд»“еә“пјҡ<br><a href="http://192.168.100.241/cloudera-repos/cdh6/6.3.2/redhat7/yum/">http://192.168.100.241/cloudera-repos/cdh6/6.3.2/redhat7/yum/</a><br>ж–№жі•жҳҜж•°жҚ®иЎЁ</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
